msgid "I'm trying to reach you. Yes, you. This is harder than you can imagine, writing words to paper that doesn't exist.\n\nWhite light. There's white light all around me.\n\nAm I alive? Am I dreaming? Are these the Colored Rooms?\n\nHelp me. I want to come home. Please.\n\nDarien"
